Cisco Routing Protocols
I IS-IS (CCIE Level)
M MPLS (Multiprotocol Layer Switching) (CCNP Level) (Label VIP)
----------------
B BGP (Border Gateway Protocol) (CCNP Level)
O OSPF (Open Shortest Path First)
D D'EIGRP (Enhanced Interior Gateway Protocol-Cisco)
---------------------------
S Static
S* Default Static



